</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[153,1222,3390,3423]" pageId="5" pageNumber="696" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="5.[153,1363,2522,3462]" box="[153,1222,3390,3423]" pageId="5" pageNumber="696">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[153,388,3390,3423]" pageId="5" pageNumber="696">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Shortridge’s Long-fingered Bat is thought to be nocturnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[154,1095,3429,3462]" pageId="5" pageNumber="696" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="5.[153,1363,2522,3462]" box="[154,1095,3429,3462]" pageId="5" pageNumber="696">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[154,856,3429,3462]" pageId="5" pageNumber="696">Movements, Home range and Social organization.</emphasis>
